Putin Judo Partner Buys Gazprom Drilling Unit, Kommersant Says

-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 
2011-03-21T05:41:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/putin-judo-partner-buys-gazprom-drilling-unit-kommersant-says.html
Arkady Rotenberg, a judo partner of
Russian Prime Minister  Vladimir Putin , bought OAO Gazprom’s
drilling unit OOO Gazprom Burenie, Kommersant reported, citing
unidentified people familiar with the matter.  State-run Gazprom, Russia’s gas exporter, said last week it
sold the unit for 4.05 billion rubles ($142 million), without
identifying the buyer.      To contact the reporter on this story:
